  m_text: '<size=24>Multi-Modal Interaction</size>

    <size=12>Poke (Press), GazePinch,
    Ray</size>


    Buttons with Microsoft Mixed Reality Design Language and other
    custom button examples using <color=#FF9E00>PressableButton.cs</color> and <color=#FF9E00>StateVisualizer.cs</color>


    PressableButtons
    use StatefulInteractable''s selection progress to model the compressability of
    a 3D pressable surface. These interactables drive selection progress through
    a combination of any number of interactors.'
